<HEADLINE>
FT  26 OCT 94 / World Stock Markets: Canada
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Toronto stocks ended down, pulled lower by a sluggish Wall Street, interest
rate jitters and a slumping US dollar, traders said.
The TSE 300 closed down 23.25 points to 4,242.77 on volume of 46.20m shares
