</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Pre-tax profits at Ocean Wilsons Holdings fell 26 per cent from Pounds 3.09m
to Pounds 2.28m in the six months to June 30.
Turnover at the investment holding and shipping company rose from Pounds
46.4m to Pounds 58.1m, an increase of 25 per cent.
Earnings per share were 4.32p (4p) and the interim dividend is unchanged at
1p.
