</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
Norsk Hydro, Norway's largest stock-listed company, yesterday reported a
rise in nine-month pre-tax profit to NKr4.75bn (Dollars 730m) from NKr4.62bn
in the same period last year, writes Karen Fossli in Oslo. The result was
