third-quarter performance by the oil and gas division.
Group nine-month sales rose NKr5.1bn to NKr51.14bn as operating profit rose
NKr2bn to NKr5.35bn. Hydro said that it had virtually completed a
far-reaching restructuring programme launched three years ago for its
magnesium and agriculture business.
